    <para id="id15121794">Let the new value of R<sub>L</sub> be R<sub>L</sub>’.</para>
    <para id="id9952712">If Q should remain unchanged then <figure id="id15114246"><media id="id15114246_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics12-615f.png" id="id15114246__onlineimage" height="31" width="101"/></media></figure></para>
