    <para id="id15258068">L=5μH . Determine C=? </para>
    <para id="id15259087">Design an Intermediate Frequency Amplifier which resonates at f<sub>o</sub>=455kHz &amp; -3 dB BW=10kHz.</para>
    <para id="id15104080">Determine C* to give a resonance frequency at fo=455kHz. [Ans: C<sub>1</sub><sup>*</sup>=24.45nF]</para>
    <figure id="id15088050">
