    <para id="id14796378">R<sub>in</sub>=1kΩ, C<sub>in</sub>=24.27nF</para>
    <para id="id15284305">Determine C<sub>1</sub> required and the resulting B.W.</para>
    <para id="id10332517">To give f<sub>o</sub>=455kHz</para>
    <figure id="id7132523">
      <media id="id7132523_media" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics16-f517.png" id="id7132523__onlineimage" height="24" width="219"/>
