    </figure>
    <para id="id10239157">The resulting resistance= 1kΩ||R<sub>in</sub>=1kΩ||1kΩ=500Ω=<figure id="id14773122"><media id="id14773122_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics18-d756.png" id="id14773122__onlineimage" height="24" width="19"/></media></figure></para>
