    <para id="id11046284">This is larger than desired. This is due to loading caused by Z<sub>in</sub> of the subsequent stage.</para>
    <para id="id11056013">Part(C) By using tapped transformer the loading can be removed. Let g<sub>m</sub>=40mA/V</para>
    <figure id="id15245808">
      <media id="id15245808_media" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 5-08f2.png" id="id15245808__onlineimage" height="306" width="299"/>
