    <para id="id9640390">To achieve a BW of 10kHz, find the value of n=?, C<sub>1</sub>=? And current gain at resonance.</para>
    <para id="id14794973">Ans:- n=1.36, C<sub>1</sub>=24.36nF, I<sub>C</sub>/I<sub>1</sub>=19.1 A/A</para>
